(2843, 'Hey!  Are you on an errand for Tirth?  If I were you I\'d get as far away from him as I could!  His mind\'s been pickled from too much drink but his magic\'s as strong as ever!', '¡Eh! ¿Estás haciéndole un recado a Tirth? ¡Yo, en tu lugar, me alejaría de él todo lo que pudiera! ¡Sus neuronas están embriagadas con tanto alcohol, pero su magia sigue tan poderosa como siempre!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
