(6028, 'TOO SOON! YOU HAVE AWAKENED ME TOO SOON, EXECUTUS! WHAT IS THE MEANING OF THIS INTRUSION???', '¡DEMASIADO PRONTO! ¡ME HAS DESPERTADO DEMASIADO PRONTO, EXECUTUS! ¿¿¿QUÉ SIGNIFICA ESTA INTROMISIÓN???', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
